            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">"Missed Call" Applications</h2>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mr-3 mt-2"></div>
              <span>Brands and Advertisers can use Free missed calls from consumers to enhance engagement and feedback.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mr-3 mt-2"></div>
              <span>The advertised numbers for "missed call" campaign can be used as a Toll-Free number for Lead Generation, Surveys, Support Campaigns, Opinion Polls & performance feedbacks.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mr-3 mt-2"></div>
              <span>Detailed Analytics and Reporting for every campaign.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-2xl p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Missed Call Apps</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

